fields.name: Created
fields.description: The datetime that the management group was created.

fields.name: DataReceived
fields.description: The last datetime that the management group received data.

fields.name: Id
fields.description: The unique ID of the management group.

fields.name: IsGateway
fields.description: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the management group is a gateway.

fields.name: Name
fields.description: The name of the management group.

fields.name: ServerCount
fields.description: The number of servers connected to the management group.

fields.name: Sku
fields.description: The SKU of System Center that is managing the management group.

fields.name: Version
fields.description: The version of System Center that is managing the management group.
